        <![CDATA[
        <b>Changes in 5.0.1</b><br/>
        [BEAM-1678] What's New page is not updated for 5.0<br/>
        <b>Changes in 5.0</b><br/>
        [BEAM-1643] Improve 'Accuracy' option in Statistics tool window<br/>
        [BEAM-1547] BEAM Help documentation for "Define Subset" dialog has not been updated<br/>
        [BEAM-1550] Link in help to general.html does not work<br/>
        ]]>
